column5: You were absolutely right telling her off and cutting her off! It's really hard to cut some one off if they're family but it's  especially hard if they're your parent. I'm really proud of you for taking that step and getting rid of a toxic relationship that only brought you pain and trauma. I hope things get better and you get to do what you love and be with people that love you.

I remember when I first started the game I made 2 very good friends, a max level fire wizard named Galen GreenEyes and his sister a max level life wizard  named Fiona. We had so much fun questing together. If I remember correctly at some point I couldn't find Galen in my friends list and his sister told me he got banned for some reason. He made a second account and we continued to play but after a while they both vanished and I've never seen them again. :(
